### 基础路径
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/users

### ============================================
### 查询所有用户（分页）
GET {{baseUrl}}?page=0&size=10&sort=id&direction=asc

### ============================================
### 按 ID 查询单个用户
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### ============================================
### 新增用户
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "新增用户",
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "address": "北京市海淀区中关村",
  "password": "password123",
  "birthday": "1993-04-20"
}

### ============================================
### 更新用户
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "更新后的张三",
  "email": "zhangsan_new@example.com",
  "address": "北京市朝阳区新地址",
  "password": "newpass123",
  "birthday": "1991-05-15"
}

### ============================================
### 删除用户
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/6
